Summary: 5 light objects, possible wedge like flying object with 5 lights. of 5 objects flying in v shape
divs: sighting detailsfirst witness outside called us to look in the sky, somewhat clouds from previous snow storm. but in a breakage could see 5 lights, possible 5 separate ufos in a v-shape, or 1 craft with 5 lights, an estimate of 5 total. flying in the same direction (no sounds that could mistake them for jet\plane). some were close and others farther above in elevation. never witnessed a ufo sighting like this before. they appeared to be cruising together, in the same direction but one after another flew by. bright, white lights, like stars. couldn't find a camera, but witnessed this sighting for almost 5 minutes.
